# Testing

## Unit and integration (Vitest)

- Command: pnpm test (sets TZ=UTC). Coverage: pnpm test:coverage
- Locations:
  - app/lib/__tests__/*.test.ts — pure utility tests
  - app/server/api/__tests__/*.test.ts — API handler tests (many fixtures)
  - app/server/services/**/__tests__ — services (Plaid, RSA/JWT, reports, forecast modules)
  - app/pages/__tests__ — simple page tests
  - app/tests/server/*.test.ts — server middleware/auth tests

If Prisma client types are missing locally, run pnpm --filter dineros-app exec prisma generate before testing (CI does this in pr.yml).

## Forecast engine tests

- Scripts:
  - pnpm test:forecast — custom TS runner (tsx services/forecast/__tests__/test-runner.ts)
  - pnpm test:forecast:unit — modernCache.unit
  - pnpm test:forecast:integration — forecastEngine.integration
  - pnpm test:forecast:all — unit + integration + runner
- Suite resides in app/server/services/forecast/__tests__ with many regression cases and snapshots

## E2E (Playwright)

- Commands:
  - pnpm test:e2e — run chromium-public and chromium-authed
  - pnpm test:e2e:update-snapshots and :staging variants
- Tests under app/tests/e2e/specs with fixtures in app/tests/e2e/setup and utils
- Visual snapshot PNGs live alongside tests; staging snapshot refresh via workflow e2e-update-staging-snapshots.yml (manual)

## Lint and pre-commit

- pnpm lint / pnpm lint-fix
- Pre-commit hooks: .pre-commit-config.yaml runs secret scanners and hygiene checks; CI runs them in pre-commit-security job

## Sonar and CodeQL

- Optional SonarQube workflow (manual trigger) produces LCOV via pnpm test:coverage
- CodeQL runs on PRs and weekly on default branch
